ing: 1 (8 ounce) wedge Brie cheese, rind removed, cut into 1-inch pieces
1/2 cup raspberry preserves, or to taste
des: "If you are looking for a quick, easy, delicious appetizer, this is for you. I've served them many times and my friends always gobble them up. Even cheese haters love this. You can find the phyllo cups in the freezer section."
ins:
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.
Arrange phyllo cups on the baking sheet. Place one piece Brie cheese in each phyllo cup. Top with 1/2 teaspoon raspberry preserves.
Bake in the preheated oven until Brie is melted, about 7 minutes.
